card_first.card_description: Siz saqlamoqchi bo'lgan videoga ega Tik Tok sahifasini oching, uning URL sini nusxa oling va SaveFrom.net ga qayting.

card_second.card_description: Sahifaning yuqorisida joylashgan kiritish qutisiga videoning URL sini joylashtiring va yuklash jarayonini boshlash uchun o'ng tomondagi tugma ustiga bosing.

card_third.card_description: Diqqat qiling, sukutiy ravishda eng yaxshi sifat avtomatik ravishda tanlanadi, lekin agar siz ma'lum bir sifat yoki formatni istasangiz, tanlash uchun bir nechta variantlar mavjud.

Section.h3: How to start Tik Tok video download with our service?
Section.p: To save TikTok video using SaveFrom.net, you need to follow three short steps. Have a look at them:

card_first.card_description: Open the Tik Tok page with a video that you want to save, copy its URL and go back to SaveFrom.net.

card_second.card_title: 2. Paste the URL onto the input field
card_second.card_description: Paste the URL of the into the input field of the top of the page and click on the right side the button to run the downloading process.

card_third.card_description: To notice that by default the best quality will be selected but if you would like a specific quality or format, there are several options you can choose from.

card_text_first.card_text_title: How to download TikTok videos online from the address bar?
card_text_first.card_text_description: Our TikTok Downloader works on any device (including, but not limited to Android, iOS, Windows, Linux, and MacOS). You do not need to install any software on your mobile phone or PC, all that you need is only a video link.
card_text_first.card_text_li: Open Tik Tok app on your phone/or Web on your browser.
card_text_first.card_text_li2: Choose whatever video you want to download.
card_text_first.card_text_li3: Click to the Share button at the right bottom.

card_text2.card_text_title: Does you store downloaded videos or keep a copy of videos?
card_text2.card_text_description: When you're downloading files, they are usually saved into whatever folder you have set as your default. Your browser normally sets this folder for you. In browser settings, you can change and choose manually the destination folder for your downloaded TikTok videos.

card_text3.card_text_title: How do I save tiktok video /download my favorite Tik Tok mp4 videos to my iPhone (IOS)?
card_text3.card_text_description: Because of Apple security policy, you can't normally download any videos Mp4 tiktok, music (Mp3), or movies to your iPhone just like you can do it with Android phones. But there are some methods to deal with it, please follow this introduction how to download TikTok video with your iPhone.
